## 7. Supabase

### Client (Expo)

- Env: **`EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`**, **`EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`** (project root `.env`).
- RLS-aware **read** of `interests` and `subtopics` matches `knowledge_schema.sql`.

### Schema (`supabase/knowledge_schema.sql`)

- **`interests`**: `id` (text PK), `label`, `sort_order`
- **`subtopics`**: `id`, `interest_id` → `interests.id`, `label`, `sort_order`
- Policies: **SELECT** allowed for anon (read-only catalog)

### Edge Function (optional)

- Name: **`generate-topic`**
- Invoked from app with JSON body: `{ interestId, interestLabel, subtopicId, subtopicLabel }`
- Should return JSON compatible with lesson UI (see `llmService` and `TopicContentScreen`).

