## 10. Native modules & Expo Go

- **Reanimated** requires `babel.config.js` to list **`react-native-reanimated/plugin` last**.
- **`index.js`** imports **`react-native-reanimated`** before other RN imports.
- **`react-native-worklets`** is pinned to **0.5.1** (with npm **overrides**) to match **Expo Go** for SDK 54. Changing Reanimated/worklets without aligning to Expo’s bundled versions may cause runtime errors (e.g. TurboModule / worklets mismatch). Custom dev clients can use versions documented for your SDK.

